Text: I dont know if it is or not but i downloaded and unrared there was a passworded file inside the rar file.

NOT password protected! bshit - just extract

but if you want to reencode to xvid/ac3 in an avi-container:
this file has AC3 Audio with a variable bitrate! (although it says CBR in for example mediainfo) means if want to mux audio/video later on into a avi-file, you'll get playback problems because of the VBR - convert to CBR with besweet to fix 

thx for sharing!
